    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "right but \"manageable\" sounds like the waste is just a math problem we've already solved. if the choice is between a slow death from climate change or a risk of some waste leaks that we can technically contain, isn't it kinda obvious which one is the smarter bet? like, can we even afford to keep debating this?",
